                    <h1 class="domdom">11</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/400">Hammer Horror&#39;s Dracula (1958)</a></h1>

                    <h2>11 Oct 2009, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>To start our Classic British Horror Season in style, we will screen the quintessentially British 'Dracula'! 
Brought to you by Hammer House of Horror in the 1950s, starring Christopher Lee as the blood sucker and Peter Cushing as possibly the best cinema Van Helsing!  
Don't dare see it&hellip;alone!

<strong></strong>Plus special guest: Cultural historian extraordinaire, Gail-Nina Anderson, will introduce and lead a discussion after the film.  </p>

